Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:18.34,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I have a big gun, I took it from my Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:21.79,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sick with Justice, I just wanna feel you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.20,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm your angel, only a ring away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:28.55,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You make me violate you, no matter who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's all up to you, no one lives forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:42.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Been burn in the hell, by all those pigs out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:45.53,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's always been hell, from when I was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:48.72,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}They make me violate them, no matter who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:52.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs79}Get down on your knees! Get a good head on your shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:55.69,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}If it's for your guys, go to the end of the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:59.00,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Do what you think, give it with dedication...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:02.27,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'll put out your misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:05.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You made a mess! For Christ sakes, this rotten world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:09.10,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Shit out of luck! Go with my vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:12.54,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Light up the fire! Right on the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:15.90,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:24.48,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a big difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This wild, dirty place is far different\Nfrom my hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. This isn't a city that\Na child like you should have to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roanapur at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You believe in your people\Nfrom home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do. I believe in her...\Nthat she'll come and save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky. To be able to feel\Nthat in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That the maid who you believe in\Nwill come for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.36,0:03:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know whether\Nit'll happen or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you must have a good family\Nfor you to have such great faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I tend to wonder how\Nmy family feels about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you miss your mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think so? If I did, I might've\Nsaid goodbye to this place long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock. That's a pointless story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a story some brat\Nwould come up with...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who chases after his mommy\Nwhen it's convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just talking about ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.19,0:04:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To see if you hold something\Nin your heart that you believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, if I'm ever kidnapped,\Nwould you come save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...waving around that\NCutlass of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't forgive you for being\Nstupid enough to get kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.64,0:04:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happened, you'd have\Nto bite off your navel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and beg forgiveness of your comrades\Nfor causing such trouble 'til you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of world this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? These are the kinda friends\NI hang out with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just the same,\Nthey're worth sticking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid. I really hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that the woman you talk about\Nis as strong as you believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This hasn't seen much action lately.\NThis Cutlass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's no point in wishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not while I'm dealing with...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a maid-obsessed brat\Nfrom the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that? "Be rude,"\Nshe says. This bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- She makes me laugh!\N- What are you gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?\NA fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am afraid I will not be able\Nto hold back. Please pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.89,0:06:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this, didn't the bar\Njust reopen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sure blasting\Nsomething flashy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Don't hold back!\NKill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do as you wish,\Nif you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not working, Bro! Why won't\Nshe fall? Is it made of kevlar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!\NYou better pay for all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite unexpectedly, we've walked\Nright into a very bad fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the fact that they're going at it\Nworks in our favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we take off\Nwhile they're busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take off? To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can go fishing at Phuket beach\Nuntil this cools down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in the mood for drinking\Nwith a gunfight on the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no Giuliano Gemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, will you hurry up and decide\Nif we're gonna shoot or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good call.\NI vote not to shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid stays here. Don't wanna go for\Na walk with a claymore landmine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's worth something, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The exit became a war-zone\Nwhile we were talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way out over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, this kid isn't money anymore.\NWe'll leave him here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.92,0:08:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, damn, fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garcia. Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move from this spot\Nuntil the gunfire dies down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it gets quiet,\Nleave this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and go home to Venezuela\Nwith your maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Roberta is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not someone capable\Nof killing. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garcia...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock! What are you waiting for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten thousand dollars for\Nthe bottles of booze...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...fifteen thousand\Nfor the furniture...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...plus twenty thousand\Nfor the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the problem is figuring out\Nwho to send the invoice to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy! Is this your doing again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do your friends\Nneed to tear up my shop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not my friends! I have\Nnothing to do with this, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foul timing to quiet down,\Nyou assholes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lagoon Company!\NWhat are you guys doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the cargo\Nyou were delivering to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold your horses!\NDon't jump to conclusions, Abrego!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the cargo doing here?!\NDid you ignore our contract?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, don't jump to conclusions!\NWe'll talk about the payment later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect to see you here,\Nyoung master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master has been very worried\Nabout you. Now, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It cannot be helped\Nif you are afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall explain myself later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good. Their eyes met.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Roberta! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back, Maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone here would\Nrather be alive than dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be crazy!\NYou're being the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you don't start shooting...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll get the young master\Nhome in one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:11:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without his brains getting splattered\Non the floor. Get what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not done with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have finished thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Una bendicion para los vivos.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Un ramo de flores para{\i0}\N{\i1}los muertos.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Spanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A blessing for the living.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- {\i1}Con una espada por la justicia.{\i0}\N- Flowers for the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- {\i1}Un castigo de muerte...{\i0}\N- Wield a sword for justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.31,0:12:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- {\i1}...para los malvados.{\i0}\N- Wield a sword for justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- {\i1}Asi Llegamos al altar de los santos.{\i0}\N- The punishment of death for the villains.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this we join\Nat the line of the saints.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Loveless family creed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot agree to your request.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will get the young master\Nhome in one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I must work\Nin accordance to this creed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of Santa Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.61,0:12:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those words...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hammer of righteousness\Nto all injustice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That... that bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stay away!\NStay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time you die!\NYou Bloodhound of Florencia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a crazy bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This makes the Battle of Khe Sanh\Nlook like a picnic in the park! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Revy all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her injuries are minor,\Nbut she has a concussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy! Say something!\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop, Roberta!\NStop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garcia...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there!\NWe're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't. I can't deal with this.\NI don't like this Roberta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I remember,\Nthose words of yours earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}El perro de cassa de Florencia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bloodhound from Florencia.\NI can't believe you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.47,0:14:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even Jesus would've noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.97,0:14:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These four years since you left\Nthe Colombian Revolutionary Army...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...everyone from the drug cartels\Nto Interpol have been after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.44,0:14:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cartels put a 400 thousand dollar\Nbounty on your head. Dead or alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luck is finally on my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I bring your head back,\NI'll be a lieutenant of the cartel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer have a reason\Nto keep you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you will excuse me, I must be\Non my way. Please accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, everybody.\NFarewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn. She's unbelievably thorough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, you bastard.\NI told you to leave the kid behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help it.\NI can't leave him in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that killed her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:15:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't be able to hear anything,\Nbut I feel something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel her footsteps getting closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her black maid's outfit\Nwill appear from that fiery exit soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then hurry up\Nand get in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Where should we go?\N- The question is, is there any place to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not likely!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a killer robot from the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing different\Nfrom the movies...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is that Schwarzenegger\Ndoesn't star in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing funny about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having trouble seeing\Nthe humor in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:17:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got her precious\Nlittle boy with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we'll head for the port!\NHurry to the Lagoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad news has a way of gathering easily\Nwithout much effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her code name is "Bloodhound".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because once she's locked\Nonto her prey, she always kills.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is gonna be a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're calling, Sergeant.\NIt's probably the worst possible news.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. She's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock! Wake Revy up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- This is no time to be comfortably asleep!\N- Revy! Revy! Revy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:17:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Corporal Menshov,\Nwhat is the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ma'am!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Yellow Flag is totally destroyed!\NThe Bloodhound and Lagoon are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, a Plymouth was seen...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...heading to the city on the main street{\i0}\N{\i1}ten minutes ago!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not leave that spot, Corporal.\NContinue gathering information.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Roger. What should{\i0}\N{\i1}I tell the owner of the bar?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him not to worry\Nabout insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am heading\Nto the city with a squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain. Are we going back to war\Nafter so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing mafia is not good.\NIt dulls your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see. But you can never\Nbe too prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We owe Lagoon.\NOr rather, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't leave this as is.\NLet's go, comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cock your hammers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.74,0:19:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me! You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now's our chance!\NHang on, Dutch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll head to the port\Nusing these back alleys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:20:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we're out to sea,\Nit doesn't matter who she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good, Benny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll lose speed this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But her radiator's shot.\NHer car won't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've paid more attention\Nto Rock's joke, Benny-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine her as an invincible\Nkiller robot or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna push it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, do whatever you can\Nto wake Revy up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need her gun\Nif we get into a shootout.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy! Revy! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.55,0:20:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Benny, turn at the next curb! Get onto\Nthe main road and go at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Benny?\NWake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit. The engine won't start.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Benny!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.49,0:21:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.06,0:21:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.56,0:23:18.56,Black Lagoon Next Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10\pos(980,916)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.53,0:23:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are no doubt the three\Nmost terrifying women in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels like Ground Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.97,0:23:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
